{"tid":1000351,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"﻿ C.朗再被仔仔拋離","createTime":"2019-01-29T11:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T06:06:44.000Z","uid":20634,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5a767ecfc326c0d80bfb34ee3f97a461af140a44","tid":1000351,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T11:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/01/29/9/947a4e443aac4899ea1720a784260b4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2019%2F01%2F29%2F9%2F947a4e443aac4899ea1720a784260b4e.jpg&h=d8c4c5a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　C.朗拿度兒子「小C朗」收穫了在祖雲達斯梯隊的第二座冠軍，他6場轟進13球。<br />\n<br />\n　　「小C朗」這次獲得的獎盃叫塞德里亞諾一月杯冠軍。他6場比賽場場入球，一共攻入13球，可以說是祖記U9奪冠的最大功臣之一。<br />\n<br />\n　　這已經是「小C朗」加盟祖記後的第二個冠軍，一舉超越老爸。C.朗拿度來到祖記後拿到了意大利超級盃冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n　　就在去年12月上旬，C.朗拿度曾發佈了一條「小C朗」和獎盃合照的狀態。"},{"pid":"8a2ef5fd92dc1cb71e6770a668fa8ff93b20ef35","tid":1000351,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T11:18:10.000Z","msg":"佢個仔同齡黎講真係超晒班"},{"pid":"6df6859c563a4b557bf77a2354265aeb69b13998","tid":1000351,"uid":171107,"like":17,"dislike":75,"score":-58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T11:21:01.000Z","msg":"個仔應該係佢老婆同美斯生既，以雞姦朗既垃圾基因生個仔無可能識入波<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j7cCSgC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj7cCSgC.jpg&h=ac0bdf23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db809f5e44c7c50374b2dad37337f1522692b584","tid":1000351,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T11:23:46.000Z","msg":"邊個先係"},{"pid":"b7755d01f6bccadba16f8222915289a2d565971c","tid":1000351,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T11:26:56.000Z","msg":"等多幾年 15-16  隨時踢到一隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7c0e9a46334259888ee74922c91c15d1026ae9","tid":1000351,"uid":37146,"like":13,"dis